0:02:44.440,0:02:45.700
I decided to do that.

0:02:45.700,0:02:48.360
I think that position is better.

0:02:48.360,0:02:55.780
That position is better to pray for the whole world.

0:02:55.780,0:03:02.800
The Bible says where there is no vision, people perish.

0:03:02.800,0:03:11.520
What has happened to my people in DRC - Congo.

0:03:11.520,0:03:22.320
I think it was three years ago when I was invited to that country, to see the president.

0:03:22.320,0:03:24.340
I prayed.

0:03:24.340,0:03:30.160
I said - to travel to DRC to see the president, the Head of State...

0:03:30.160,0:03:33.840
