Jesus knew he would not be able to succeed alone; that is why He had 12 disciples.

0:26:45.080,0:26:49.800
He knew no one can go it alone.

0:26:49.800,0:26:57.000
He knew that as a Saviour he had to look for people to follow Him.

0:26:57.000,0:27:00.180
Even among them - you know what happened.

0:27:00.180,0:27:05.120
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:27:05.120,0:27:11.940
You know what is happening all over the world - not only in politics; even in the house of God.

0:27:11.940,0:27:16.700
The cause of churches collapsing is what I am talking about now.

0:27:16.700,0:27:27.740
They cannot point to a man of their own heart to do this for them and they cannot do it alone.

0:27:27.740,0:27:39.400
Instead, they use their enemies to do this and their enemies crumble their vision.

0:27:39.400,0:27:44.580
You know what is happening to your business; you cannot do it alone.

0:27:44.580,0:27:50.520
At a time, you wanted to expand but no one was there to help you.

0:27:50.520,0:27:53.580
You cannot be in two places at the same time.

0:27:53.580,0:27:55.840
You continue to expand where you are.

0:27:55.840,0:28:08.960
When you begin to be too popular in a certain place, attack and persecution start.

0:28:08.960,0:28:13.720
This is why today you see millionaires who were up there crumble

0:28:13.720,0:28:17.920
because they could not find people to carry out their vision.

0:28:17.920,0:28:30.160
Branches of their companies – the people that represented those branches crumbled their vision.

0:28:30.160,0:28:40.580
When you start to think about expanding - "No, let me remain where I am".

0:28:40.580,0:28:46.680
Success does not permit that; success wants to explode.

0:28:46.680,0:28:50.820
You can’t light a candle and put it under the roof.

0:28:50.820,0:28:54.140
You must bring the candle out and let the world see it.

0:28:54.140,0:28:57.740
If you put a candle under the roof, it will burn the house.

0:28:57.740,0:29:04.340
If you say you are afraid and you camp that success, you will explode with the success.

0:29:04.340,0:29:07.740
The success will consume you.

0:29:07.740,0:29:13.060
So, now, what is the way out?

0:29:13.060,0:29:23.320
Faith is something that comes spontaneously, naturally – that is faith.

0:29:23.320,0:29:25.380
What is the way out?

0:29:25.380,0:29:34.500
The way out is . as you are growing, take time to train people and impart to people.

0:29:34.500,0:29:39.860
If not, by the time you finish growing and become an iroko tree,

0:29:39.860,0:29:49.040
you will not see anyone to help you; you will use your enemy as a helper.

0:29:49.040,0:29:53.900
Jesus took time to train people, to impart in them.

0:29:53.900,0:29:57.540
And even then - He was betrayed.

0:29:57.540,0:30:05.920
But at last, He made the best out of His people.

0:30:05.920,0:30:10.260
Take your time to train people.

0:30:10.260,0:30:12.380
What do I mean by training?

0:30:12.380,0:30:15.320
Allow them to see what you are doing.

0:30:15.320,0:30:18.900
Let them see what you are doing, so they can do the same.

0:30:18.900,0:30:24.280
As they see what you are doing, your enemies among them will give way

0:30:24.280,0:30:28.460
and those men after your own heart will continue to follow you.

0:30:28.460,0:30:34.500
Finally when you get there, they can be there to carry the vision.

0:30:34.500,0:30:39.220
This is what the world is facing today; there is crisis in this world.

0:30:39.220,0:30:41.160
That is why there are no new things coming.

0:30:41.160,0:30:45.000
I told you last time that we are running out of ideas.

0:30:45.000,0:30:48.700
The world is running out of ideas.

0:30:48.700,0:30:51.620
There is no new vision - nothing new.

0:30:51.620,0:30:55.900
Science is running out of ideas.

0:30:55.900,0:31:00.340
There is no new idea because they are dying with their own ideas.

0:31:00.340,0:31:03.280
They cannot impart those ideas to people.

0:31:03.280,0:31:07.220
They don't have people of their own heart to work with them.

0:31:07.220,0:31:10.160
If you continue to carry it alone, you will get tired.

0:31:10.160,0:31:13.880
If this body is tired, you cannot carry out the vision again.

0:31:13.880,0:31:18.400
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:31:18.400,0:31:36.940
So, like I have said; as you are growing, take your time to grow others.

0:31:36.940,0:31:42.240
It's not just to be using them and then giving them money.

0:31:42.240,0:31:43.660
We are not talking about money.

0:31:43.660,0:31:47.760
You have people working with you - you can pay them a lot of money - that is not the issue.

0:31:47.760,0:31:53.020
Money cannot make the vision we are talking about; it's all about sincerity.

0:31:53.020,0:31:58.640
You say, "I pay them. I give them huge money. They work with me..."

0:31:58.640,0:32:02.120
We are not talking of working with you and giving them money.

0:32:02.120,0:32:05.620
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:32:05.620,0:32:17.880
OK, if you are bigger than this tomorrow, how will you maintain that grace?

0:32:17.880,0:32:24.760
You alone cannot maintain that position; you need someone to…

0:32:24.760,0:32:31.160
And you don’t have any men of your own heart;

0:32:31.160,0:32:38.860
you finally find yourself using your enemy to maintain your vision.

0:32:38.860,0:32:44.620
Look at universities all over the world or in Nigeria... just university in Nigeria alone.

0:32:44.620,0:32:45.820
Do you know what is happening?

0:32:45.820,0:32:50.720
Those best universities in the world that we know about in Nigeria.

0:32:50.720,0:32:55.280
When you go to their premises or campus, see what is happening...

0:32:55.280,0:32:57.060
It is not an issue of money.

0:32:57.060,0:33:00.800
But we keep shouting, "Money! There is no money to develop".

0:33:00.800,0:33:03.300
It is not an issue of money!

0:33:03.300,0:33:06.180
I know money is very important.

0:33:06.180,0:33:08.520
It is not an issue of money.

0:33:08.520,0:33:18.840
If you look at first class students - very brilliant - and you send them to another country for a program

0:33:18.840,0:33:22.620
and another country sends their first class students to that country...

0:33:22.620,0:33:30.120
When they come back, they will raise the standard here.

0:33:30.120,0:33:33.800
How much does it take to send people to...

0:33:33.800,0:33:35.260
And you keep saying, "Money money money".

0:33:35.260,0:33:43.140
If there is money and no brain, can money work?

0:33:43.140,0:33:45.740
Brain is dying - we are running out of ideas.

0:33:45.740,0:33:46.880
You talk of money.

0:33:46.880,0:33:56.340
When there is no idea, money is dead; money is useless.

0:33:56.340,0:34:05.800
If a man without an idea has money - it is like "mental people" having money - the crazy man.

0:34:05.800,0:34:14.940
It is like a very rich man suddenly having a mental problem - it is equal to a rich man running out of ideas.

0:34:14.940,0:34:17.720
When you don't have ideas, the money is useless.

0:34:17.720,0:34:22.900
It is an idea that makes use of money; it is an idea that spends money.

0:34:22.900,0:34:24.400
Where are we going?

0:34:24.400,0:34:25.880
That is our education.

0:34:25.880,0:34:34.120
Not only in Nigeria - all over the world - just like that.

0:34:34.120,0:34:41.840
There are some faculties at universities which need to be increased in number.

0:34:41.840,0:34:45.120
But because you are looking for money, you just want to have a university

0:34:45.120,0:34:50.860
and you don't mind any course they study. You need money from students.

0:34:50.860,0:34:57.600
Whereas there are some important faculties that can build the nation.

0:34:57.600,0:35:00.360
Until we begin to separate those faculties...

0:35:00.360,0:35:06.700
You have this university, college of medicine; you have this university, law school...

0:35:06.700,0:35:12.640
No. You bring all together which destroys university.

0:35:12.640,0:35:18.580
There are some students there that "have no brain" - they just go to university to study any course.

0:35:18.580,0:35:22.580
Compare it to a subject where you have to have a brain to study it.

0:35:22.580,0:35:31.740
You must separate these students in order to build the nation.

0:35:31.740,0:35:35.120
But the university of this or college...

0:35:35.120,0:35:38.620
When you look at those faculties, they seem to be useless.

0:35:38.620,0:35:42.180
These are the faculties that you only spend money on.

0:35:42.180,0:35:47.920
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:35:47.920,0:35:52.500
When you look at the nation, you will be able to know what the nation needs at that time.

0:35:52.500,0:35:58.120
What does this nation, your country, need at this time?

0:35:58.120,0:36:10.300
Not until we begin to sort out those faculties, universities - separate them, put them where they belong.

0:36:10.300,0:36:12.920
The importance of those faculties...

0:36:12.920,0:36:17.260
Know how you can get the money to raise the standard of those faculties to build the nation.

0:36:17.260,0:36:21.280
When you build those faculties, you are building the nation.

0:36:21.280,0:36:24.860
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:36:24.860,0:36:28.400
Many parents don't know their right and left.

0:36:28.400,0:36:31.520
They just want their children to go to university.

0:36:31.520,0:36:32.980
Fine.

0:36:32.980,0:36:40.280
We get money but money without ideas is useless.

0:36:40.280,0:36:48.820
So, I think - what we are facing today is that we lack ideas.

0:36:48.820,0:36:52.860
People lack ideas but have money.

0:36:52.860,0:36:54.300
You can't eat your money.

0:36:54.300,0:36:59.680
Your money is not valuable without ideas.

0:36:59.680,0:37:06.220
When you ask people a simple question today, they will complain about their government.

0:37:06.220,0:37:09.320
Our government doesn't do this or that.

0:37:09.320,0:37:14.140
When you don't run out of ideas, you do not have any business with the government -

0:37:14.140,0:37:21.340
even the government will want you to help the nation if you have not run out of ideas.

0:37:21.340,0:37:24.560
It is when we run out of ideas that we begin to complain about the government.

0:37:24.560,0:37:32.320
No money to do this or that - because we are running out of ideas.

0:37:32.320,0:37:35.940
You can be so great without the government.

0:37:35.940,0:37:39.620
The government will now turn to you for help.

0:37:39.620,0:37:43.900
There is a lot of burden on the government because everybody depends on the government.

0:37:43.900,0:37:47.140
That is why the world is collapsing.

0:37:47.140,0:37:52.220
You depend on the government of your nation to live, which is wrong.

0:37:52.220,0:37:55.740
Because we are running out of ideas.

0:37:55.740,0:38:00.480
Without a contract from the government, you cannot live.

0:38:00.480,0:38:03.700
Without government supporting business, you cannot live.

0:38:03.700,0:38:09.940
If there is no budget to give money to everybody, you complain.

0:38:09.940,0:38:13.800
This is what we depend on because we are running out of ideas.

0:38:13.800,0:38:19.820
Not until people have ideas, you cannot leave this pitiful life.

0:38:19.820,0:38:26.360
When trouble comes to the government, it will affect you.

0:38:26.360,0:38:30.300
You have to look beyond.

0:38:30.300,0:38:32.160
Yes.

0:38:32.160,0:38:34.740
Rise up for prayer.

0:38:34.740,0:38:39.580
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:38:39.580,0:38:50.840
What is the cause of man running out of ideas?

0:38:50.840,0:38:58.000
When you run out of ideas, you begin to look at others to reason and think,

0:38:58.000,0:39:06.420
compare yourself to others and measure yourself with others, you are running out of ideas.

0:39:06.420,0:39:12.940
You say, "This man is slim - I want to be slim. Look at the hair of this woman - I want the same haircut.

0:39:12.940,0:39:17.800
I saw a posh car last week - I want to buy the same car".

0:39:17.800,0:39:20.120
You are running out of ideas.

0:39:20.120,0:39:30.940
You begin to imitate others to live, talk and even pray.

0:39:30.940,0:39:38.720
You look at what people say - you want to say the same because you run out of ideas.

0:39:38.720,0:39:42.800
When you run out of ideas, your money is not your money;

0:39:42.800,0:39:47.580
your money is someone else's money.

0:39:47.580,0:39:49.580
Are you with me?

0:39:49.580,0:39:54.900
When you run out of ideas, your possession is not your possession;

0:39:54.900,0:39:59.120
it is someone else's possession because you don’t know the use of it.

0:39:59.120,0:40:03.360
Someone else will be using your possessions, enjoying what you have.

0:40:03.360,0:40:08.300
You go for a medical check-up - little time - sickness, disease, this, that...

0:40:08.300,0:40:10.900
They give you this; they give you chieftaincy.

0:40:10.900,0:40:15.560
When there is no money, you are not given the chieftaincy. When money comes, they call you for chieftaincies.

0:40:15.560,0:40:22.680
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:40:22.680,0:40:27.900
Time to ask yourself, "Why did they not call me for chieftaincy when I didn't have money?

0:40:27.900,0:40:30.280
But now I have money and they call me for chieftaincy".

0:40:30.280,0:40:33.020
You should know that something is wrong somewhere.

0:40:33.020,0:40:36.260
"I was not sick when I did not have enough.

0:40:36.260,0:40:38.620
But now that I have enough, I'm sick."

0:40:38.620,0:40:40.880
What do you think happened then?

0:40:40.880,0:40:45.400
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:40:45.400,0:40:53.980
"People call me to invite me, to visit them, to come to a party, from all over the world, because I have...

0:40:53.980,0:40:56.200
How do they know that I have?

0:40:56.200,0:41:00.900
When I didn't have, nobody invited me, nobody wanted to be my friend."

0:41:00.900,0:41:03.180
Can't you ask yourself, "Why?"

0:41:03.180,0:41:07.880
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:41:07.880,0:41:14.640
So much responsibility - and this responsibility will take you away from God.

0:41:14.640,0:41:16.460
Take note of this once again.

0:41:16.460,0:41:26.460
When you run out of ideas, your possession is someone else's possession.

0:41:26.460,0:41:35.040
To run out of ideas means when you cannot think right at the right time or do things at the right time.

0:41:35.040,0:41:41.340
You may do them but not at the right time.

0:41:41.340,0:41:45.580
You move - it is right that you must move but it is at the wrong time.

0:41:45.580,0:41:50.080
To do things at the right time gives result.

0:41:50.080,0:41:53.180
There is a time for everything.

0:41:53.180,0:41:59.620
If you are not standing up for prayer now at the right time, it means God will not connect with us.

0:41:59.620,0:42:01.320
You pray at the wrong time.

0:42:01.320,0:42:06.160
It's right you are praying but are you praying at the right time?

0:42:06.160,0:42:11.440
The Holy Spirit intercedes for us; we don’t know how to pray.

0:42:11.440,0:42:14.900
You cannot just stand up and just say, "I want to pray".

0:42:14.900,0:42:20.300
If I have faith in God, there will be what?

0:42:20.300,0:42:25.140
There will be work that corresponds with the faith.

0:42:25.140,0:42:36.420
Tell your neighbour, "If there is faith, there will be work that corresponds with the faith".

0:42:36.420,0:42:37.200
Again.

0:42:37.200,0:42:41.720
If there is faith, there will be work that corresponds with the faith.

0:42:41.720,0:42:42.780
I cannot hear you.

0:42:42.780,0:42:48.000
If there is faith, there will be work that corresponds with the faith.

0:42:48.000,0:42:50.460
If there is no work that corresponds with the faith...

0:42:50.460,0:42:56.140
If work is different from faith - that is, you have bad work.

0:42:56.140,0:43:01.100
The work you are doing is not good.

0:43:01.100,0:43:05.060
But you have faith - that cannot correspond.

0:43:05.060,0:43:13.040
If there is faith, there will be work that corresponds with the faith.

0:43:13.040,0:43:15.880
It is like a magnet and a nail.

0:43:15.880,0:43:22.320
You have a nail here and you have a magnet here - if you bring them close, they will...

0:43:22.320,0:43:25.480
You can see - magnet.

0:43:25.480,0:43:30.080
But if it is not a nail, it will not...

0:43:30.080,0:43:37.840
If there is faith, there will be work that corresponds with the faith.

0:43:37.840,0:43:46.900
If not, you will continue to say, "I am a Christian. I have faith" but this work doesn't correspond with...

0:43:46.900,0:43:49.900
This is why when we pray today, our prayer goes nowhere.

0:43:49.900,0:43:51.760
We talk to ourselves when we are praying.

0:43:51.760,0:43:56.740
"In the name of Jesus" - you are talking to yourself.

0:43:56.740,0:43:57.660
Tell your neighbour again:

0:43:57.660,0:44:12.600
"If there is faith, there will be work that corresponds with the faith."

0:44:12.600,0:44:18.060
This is what I mean by our work proves our faith.

0:44:18.060,0:44:24.260
This is what I mean by our work completes or perfects our faith.

0:44:24.260,0:44:28.200
If your work does not correspond with your faith, you are faithless.

0:44:28.200,0:44:31.520
The faith you are talking about is not faith in God.

0:44:31.520,0:44:41.880
There are all kinds of faith but I am talking about faith in God.

0:44:41.880,0:44:52.080
Have faith in God
All things are possible

0:44:52.080,0:44:53.320
Again.

0:44:53.320,0:45:06.840
Have faith in God
All things are possible

0:45:06.840,0:45:08.180
Again.

0:45:08.180,0:45:23.780
Have faith in God
All things are possible

0:45:23.780,0:45:25.660
That is the faith I'm talking about.

0:45:25.660,0:45:29.340
Have it in God - the Bible talks about it in Mark.

0:45:29.340,0:45:47.480
If there is faith - if you claim you have this faith, there will be work that corresponds with the faith.

0:45:47.480,0:45:52.520
You know where your problem comes from now.

0:45:52.520,0:45:56.560
You can know where your problem comes from.

0:45:56.560,0:46:06.000
Right now, it's a matter of talking with all your heart, confessing with all your heart.

0:46:06.000,0:46:14.460
Ask God for His grace; you need His grace.

0:46:14.460,0:46:16.700
Open your lips - prayer.

0:46:16.700,0:46:31.420
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:46:31.420,0:46:42.480
Ask God for His grace.

0:46:42.480,0:46:53.940
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:46:53.940,0:46:57.420
In the mighty name of Jesus Christ we pray.

0:46:57.420,0:46:59.540
[Amen.]

0:46:59.540,0:47:05.700
Out of the message I gave you today, take note of one point.

0:47:05.700,0:47:08.920
This is the mistake we are doing.

0:47:08.920,0:47:15.800
You never believed that your enemy can give you trillions of dollars and yet be your enemy.

0:47:15.800,0:47:23.360
You believed that someone giving you a billion dollars loves you with all his heart.

0:47:23.360,0:47:31.420
Your enemy can give you trillions of dollars and yet be your enemy.

0:47:31.420,0:47:33.360
But you don't know that.

0:47:33.360,0:47:44.880
To you; you consider someone giving you so much a man of your own heart - no, my brother!

0:47:44.880,0:47:47.540
How do you run your business then?

0:47:47.540,0:47:52.040
You run it without ideas because you need money.

0:47:52.040,0:47:56.220
Somebody giving you money becomes your dear friend.

0:47:56.220,0:48:03.280
We don't go beyond to ask God, "Who is giving me money?"

0:48:03.280,0:48:08.140
Do you know that your enemy can establish you?

0:48:08.140,0:48:15.060
If you know that raise up your hand.

0:48:15.060,0:48:25.900
An enemy can establish you for reasons known to him.

0:48:25.900,0:48:29.680
Oh my God.

0:48:29.680,0:48:34.140
There are many things that you don't know.

0:48:34.140,0:48:37.880
You don't know because you are a business man.

0:48:37.880,0:48:40.480
You are a politician.

0:48:40.480,0:48:45.440
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:48:45.440,0:48:50.720
This is the reason why you are facing many things.

0:48:50.720,0:48:55.800
Think about your track record from the beginning.

0:48:55.800,0:48:58.420
Sit down and think about your life.

0:48:58.420,0:49:04.160
You will begin to agree with me.

0:49:04.160,0:49:11.580
You don't believe that people that have done so much for you can turn round to be your enemies.

0:49:11.580,0:49:17.580
They seem to be giving you so much, they seem to establish you - they later turn to be your enemies

0:49:17.580,0:49:21.860
at a difficult time, at the time you need them.

0:49:21.860,0:49:35.980
The SCOAN Sunday Service

0:49:35.980,0:49:42.740
I don't want you to get to Heaven before you understand all this.

0:49:42.740,0:49:47.480
